<F P=106> [By reporters Zhang Jimin (1728 4949 3046) and Qin Chun </F>
(4440 2504)] 
  [Text] Beijing, 7 Jun (XINHUA) -- Zhu Guangya was elected 
president of the Chinese Academy of Engineerng [CAE] at the 
plenary session of the CAE's academicians' conference today. 
Zhu Gaofeng, Shi Changxu, Pan Jiazheng, and Lu Liangshu were 
elected vice presidents. 
