Guangya, Zhu Gaofeng, Song Jian, Zhang Wei, Zhang Guangdou, Lu 
Yuanjiu, Fang Weitang, Lin Hua, Luo Peilin, Ji Guobiao, Jin 
Yilian, Zhou Ganzhi, Hou Xianglin, Yao Fusheng, Qian Yi, Yin 
Ruiyu, and Pan Jiazheng. Zhu Guangya is the executive chairman 
of the CAS' Presidium. 

