(5685 2139 2251)] 
  [Text] Yesterday evening, Abulaiti Abudurexiti, Xinjiang 
Autonomous Regional People's Government chairman, and (Kim 
Kap-yon), president of the Korea-China Group [KCG] of the ROK, 
signed a letter of intent for long-term economic cooperation 
