BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, June 9 (XINHUA) -- Wen Jiabao, an 
alternate member of the Political Bureau of the Communist Party 
of China (CPC) Central Committee, met a delegation from the 
Communist Party of India (Marxist) headed by Harkishan Singh 
Surjeet, general secretary of the party here this afternoon. 
  During the meeting, Wen, who is also a member of the 
