<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Damascus, 7 Jun (XINHUA) -- New Chinese Ambassador 
Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary Li Qingyu [2621 3237 3768) 
presented his credentials to President al-Asad here this 
