Kim the results of his talks with DPRK leaders. 
  Carter said on Thursday: "My hope during this private visit 
is to discuss some of the important issues of the day with 
leaders of the area." 
  Carter has been active in resolving conflicts in Panama, 
Nicaragua and Sudan, among others. 

